	<h1 class="title">「酸汤鱼经济学」烟草税貌似正义，但不能帮人戒烟</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/3891/small/3891.jpg?1418027288" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">酸汤鱼 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-21 08:09:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/11039/medium/11039.jpg?1436643377" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


